      "message": "Looks like it\u0027s possible based on https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/src/third_party/googletest/src/googletest/include/gtest/internal/gtest-internal.h?l\u003d706\u0026rcl\u003df2fb48c3b3d79a75a88a99fba6576b25d42ec528 (note the conditional slash if \"prefix\" is empty string), but I didn\u0027t actually see any examples of type parametrized tests that don\u0027t have an instantiation.",
